content:
Understood. I'll create a promotional image for the discussion panel, formatted as a digital flyer. First, I need a few more details to get the design right.
<question-form id="discovery" title="Quick brief — 30 seconds">
{
  "description": "I'll use this to refine the design of the promo image. Skip what doesn't apply — I'll fill defaults.",
  "questions": [
    {
      "id": "panel_topic",
      "label": "What is the specific topic of the discussion panel?",
      "type": "text",
      "required": true,
      "placeholder": "e.g., 'The Future of AI in Small Business'"
    },
    {
      "id": "brand",
      "label": "Brand context",
      "type": "radio",
      "options": [
        { "label": "Pick a visual direction for me", "value": "pick_direction" },
        { "label": "I have a brand spec — I'll share it", "value": "brand_spec" },
        { "label": "Match a reference site / screenshot — I'll attach it", "value": "reference_match" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
</question-form>
